videos.description: Mekhi Sargent takes the handoff and cuts for a 3-yard touchdown to extend Iowa's lead over Illinois in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Iowa runs in short TD in 2nd

videos.description: A.J. Epenesa rushes the edge to block the Illinois punt and Nick Niemann scoops it up to begin Iowa's drive in the red zone.
videos.headline: Iowa blocks punt to set up short field

videos.description: Nate Stanley hits T.J. Hockenson in stride up the sideline for a 37-yard touchdown, adding onto Iowa's lead over Illinois.
videos.headline: Stanley extends Iowa's lead with TD pass

videos.description: Kyle Groeneweg fields a punt and returns it 61 yards for a touchdown to give Iowa a 42-0 lead over Illinois to open the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Iowa takes punt to the house
